text: Modesta Uka (born 23 May 1999) is a Kosovar footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Uka has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:ÖFB-Frauenliga players Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Austria Category:Kosovan expatriate sportspeople in Austria Category:SK Sturm Graz (women) players
title: Modesta Uka
